{
  "stem": "18061.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Then we had also an institution for a few people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They had no place where to sleep.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They call it Hachnasat Orchim That is, I guess, people that came from somewhere, people, beggars.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They have no place where to go.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They slept over there, and they had their meals over there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It was supported by the Jewish people, by the richer Jewish people, who could afford.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And there was also sent-- set a tax from the kehilla.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Kehilla means the committee of the Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They taxed the people-- they know who so much and so much-- to help out the poor people.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I had-- I had a Jewish friend.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My relation-- my special relation was very good, excellent was.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Before the war, I had a lot of friends.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We went out together.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And even I will tell a story about the Holocaust.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I will tell you the story about non-Jewish people, which I have.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The-- the Polish people, which they didn't live in our section, in the Jewish section mostly.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were-- no, we had fights with them, throwing stones, and calling names each other.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Oh, we went through-- we went through that, because they were agitated by priest, by teachers, anti-Semitic.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I would say it wasn't even the fault of the kids.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They heard of it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they didn't understand anything else.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But the Jewish people killed Jesus, which nobody of us know what that is.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And from that, it started, the anti-Semitism about the young people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's hard for me to describe myself.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was more than the shy side.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah, I was more shy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I involved in-- in sport.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mostly soccer games.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That most-- most of it.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
